":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T02:20:18.000Z","msg":"太安樓?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T05:36:38.000Z","msg":"垃圾地方，貴，污糟，唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfba8f265c8129a37712d54de3e975891295acd1","tid":2094723,"uid":112828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T05:37:54.000Z","msg":"如果你有錢<br />\n可以搵條僻D既街<br />\n買起哂D鋪再做起佢<br />\n<br />\n成功例子有盛智文既蘭桂坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽講深水埗有個位都有cafe area 做起緊"},{"pid":"de937ef815a57cb454187dcc9277c000f014d46d","tid":2094723,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T05:39:53.000Z","msg":"衛生 環境 商家佬"},{"pid":"e4a8fd47c0771cfb5e7a508a2f288f4dd55056af","tid":2094723,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T05:48:57.000Z","msg":"租金<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c41c473e543c6ed85daa722e3340bc8a04a3f0","tid":2094723,"uid":127955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T05:56:52.000Z","msg":"小食街。食客，仲要係區外人就爽<br />\n附近居民反感大到你唔信<br />\n衞生環境（噪音）品流複雜每一樣野都夠ban到行一行<br />\n<br />\n你話放起垃圾桶附近？當垃圾量多左兩倍就要多2倍資源去清垃圾，區議會起嗰part就落多2倍budget。政府野一要用多錢就要解釋這是否必需增加的計劃。<br />\n<br />\n人流多成點，消防過唔過到又要度。過唔到消防柱位嗰d可能建要加<br />\n<br />\n你話搵條街做小食街係咪咁撚難<br />\n係。真係好撚難。"},{"pid":"3fbacb938c2434b31c2027a2b8ba572fbff07775","tid":2094723,"uid":112828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T06:00:08.000Z","msg":"有冇人知紅磡加太賀嗰頭而家做成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f5e05fdf40d888ff594996708e63d645450585","tid":2094723,"uid":63977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5786e0f723559701e3e7e066f61c3a01d2f47510","tid":2094723,"uid":134683,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"22400574d959cf7e8d35472ff3d0c9392cbf9ae8","tid":2094723,"uid":102700,"like":120,"dislike":1